	<h1 class="title">药企到底付给医生多少钱？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/16232/small/16232.jgp?1419796799" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">Charles Ornstein, Ryann Grochowski Jones and Eric Sagara</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2014-10-04 09:13:15 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/2678/medium/2678.jpg?1436653397" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


